Quick compilation instructions (April 2022):

For Linux Mint / Ubuntu 20.04.

1) install libao-dev and mpg123-dev 
2) Install a modified version of libforms-dev from :
   https://github.com/pmxy/XForms_FIXED_2022_04_28/blob/master/libforms-dev_1.2.4-1ubuntu1_amd64.deb
2) Install a modified version of libforms-bin from :
   https://github.com/pmxy/XForms_FIXED_2022_04_28/blob/master/libforms-bin_1.2.4-1ubuntu1_amd64.deb
4) ./configure
    OR
   if you want a pritev install in $HOME/.local :
  ./configure --prefix=$HOME/.local --exec-prefix==$HOME/.local --bindir==$HOME/.local/bin
5) make
6) make install
5) Extract mpg123-1.22.2.tar.bz2 and enter the directory


   Or just copy impfe somewhere in your path. impfe.music.mp3 must go in /bin

Default server port for Imperium is 3458
